name_pretty: Google Cloud Gaming Allocationendpoint V1alpha API
ruby-cloud-description: google-cloud-gaming-allocationendpoint-v1alpha is the official client library for the Google Cloud Gaming Allocationendpoint V1alpha API. Note that google-cloud-gaming-allocationendpoint-v1alpha is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-gaming-allocationendpoint instead. See the readme for more details.
